    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "🔍 AI Competitor Intelligence Monitor Workflow\n\nScrapes competitor websites every Monday, uses AI to \nanalyze positioning, pricing and feature changes, \nsends urgent alerts or weekly summaries automatically.\n\nNodes:\n**Step 1**\n▶ Schedule Trigger — Runs every Monday at 8am\n\n**Step 2**\n🌐 HTTP Request — Scrapes Zapier pricing page\n\n**Step 3**\n⚙️ Extract Key Info — Extracts features prices and content\n\n**Step 4**\n🤖 OpenAI — Analyzes competitor positioning and changes\n\n**Step 5**\n⚙️ CleanUp — Cleans and structures AI analysis output\n\n**Step 6**\n🔀 IF — Checks if urgent alert is needed\n\n**Step 7**\n✅ TRUE: Gmail — Sends urgent competitor alert draft\n\n**Step 8**\n✅ TRUE: Code in JavaScript — Prepares logging data\n\n**Step 9**\n✅ TRUE: Google Sheets — Logs intelligence report\n\n**Step 10**\n❌ FALSE: Gmail1 — Sends weekly intelligence summary\n\n**Step 11**\n❌ FALSE: Code in JavaScript1 — Prepares logging data\n\n**Step 12**\n❌ FALSE: Google Sheets1 — Logs intelligence report",
